[h2]For Stellaris: 4.1.*[/h2]

Adds many new [b]Planetary Wonders[/b], with custom icons, images and events.
Wonders are buildings that take up a district slot, a lot of resources and time, but provide many jobs and bonuses.
Only one allowed per planet, but more can be unlocked by the new Ascension Perk.
Only Void Dwellers (or with Voidborne) can build them on Habitats.
Every Wonder is planet-unique, and some are empire-unique.

